title: War of the Roses: She planted what in his suitcase??
description: Kylie and her boyfriend live together and recently she found lipstick on a cup and an earring in the couch, both of which were not from her.  She confronted her boyfriend and he says he doesn't know where any of it came from.  SO, she took things into her own hands to try to catch him cheating but he still didn't admit to it, so now he's turning to us to do War of the Roses.
